# 😈 Troll Start Button – Infinite Chaos Prank

A fun and chaotic browser prank where the “Start” button refuses to be clicked 😼

## 🎮 Features

* 🏃 Button runs away when cursor gets close
* 📉 Button shrinks every time you try to click
* 🔊 Funny sound effects (meow + chaos vibes)
* 😂 Emoji rain for maximum trolling
* 📳 Screen shake + glitch effects
* 🖥️ Auto fullscreen (for full immersion)
* ⏳ Fake loading screen to build suspense

## 🤡 What Happens?

You try to click the button…
It moves.
You try again… it gets smaller.
Then the screen starts shaking, emojis fall everywhere, and it mocks you:

**“meh kaha ladle 😼 meow ghop ghop ghop 😂😂😂”**

Good luck catching it 😏

## 🚀 How to Run

1. Download or clone this repository
2. Open `index.html` in your browser
3. Try clicking the button (if you can 😈)

